---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Services" description="Professional cybersecurity services including CVE scans, penetration testing, and EN 18031-1 compliance testing">
	<section class="page-header">
		<div class="container">
			<h1>Our Services</h1>
			<p>Comprehensive cybersecurity solutions to protect your organization</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="service-detail" id="cve">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="service-content">
				<div class="service-text">
					<h2>üîç CVE Vulnerability Scanning</h2>
					<p class="lead">Stay ahead of threats with comprehensive Common Vulnerabilities and Exposures (CVE) scanning across your entire infrastructure.</p>
					
					<h3>What We Offer</h3>
					<ul class="feature-list">
						<li><strong>Automated Continuous Scanning:</strong> 24/7 monitoring of your systems for newly discovered vulnerabilities</li>
						<li><strong>Comprehensive Coverage:</strong> Scan networks, applications, operating systems, and third-party components</li>
						<li><strong>Prioritized Risk Assessment:</strong> CVSS-based scoring with business context to prioritize critical threats</li>
						<li><strong>Actionable Reports:</strong> Detailed vulnerability reports with remediation steps and timelines</li>
						<li><strong>Threat Intelligence Integration:</strong> Real-time updates from global threat databases</li>
						<li><strong>Compliance Mapping:</strong> Align findings with regulatory requirements</li>
					</ul>

					<h3>Our Scanning Process</h3>
					<ol class="process-list">
						<li><strong>Asset Discovery:</strong> Identify all systems, applications, and devices in your environment</li>
						<li><strong>Vulnerability Detection:</strong> Deep scanning using industry-leading tools and CVE databases</li>
						<li><strong>Analysis & Prioritization:</strong> Risk assessment based on exploitability and business impact</li>
						<li><strong>Reporting:</strong> Clear, executive-level summaries and detailed technical reports</li>
						<li><strong>Remediation Support:</strong> Guidance and support for addressing identified vulnerabilities</li>
					</ol>

					<div class="cta-box">
						<h3>Pricing</h3>
						<p>Custom pricing based on infrastructure size and scan frequency. Starting from $2,500/month for SMBs.</p>
						<a href="/quote" class="btn-primary">Request a Quote</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="service-detail alt-bg" id="pentest">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="service-content">
				<div class="service-text">
					<h2>üõ°Ô∏è Penetration Testing</h2>
					<p class="lead">Simulate real-world attacks to identify security weaknesses before malicious actors exploit them.</p>
					
					<h3>Testing Methodologies</h3>
					<ul class="feature-list">
						<li><strong>Network Penetration Testing:</strong> External and internal network infrastructure assessment</li>
						<li><strong>Web Application Testing:</strong> OWASP Top 10 and beyond for web-based applications</li>
						<li><strong>Mobile Application Testing:</strong> iOS and Android app security assessments</li>
						<li><strong>API Security Testing:</strong> REST, SOAP, and GraphQL API vulnerability analysis</li>
						<li><strong>Cloud Security Assessment:</strong> AWS, Azure, and GCP configuration and security testing</li>
						<li><strong>Social Engineering:</strong> Phishing simulations and security awareness testing</li>
						<li><strong>Wireless Network Testing:</strong> Wi-Fi and Bluetooth security assessments</li>
					</ul>

					<h3>Testing Approach</h3>
					<ol class="process-list">
						<li><strong>Planning & Reconnaissance:</strong> Define scope, objectives, and gather intelligence</li>
						<li><strong>Scanning & Enumeration:</strong> Identify potential attack vectors and vulnerabilities</li>
						<li><strong>Exploitation:</strong> Attempt to exploit vulnerabilities in controlled manner</li>
						<li><strong>Post-Exploitation:</strong> Assess the extent of potential compromise</li>
						<li><strong>Reporting:</strong> Comprehensive report with findings, evidence, and recommendations</li>
						<li><strong>Remediation Verification:</strong> Re-test after fixes to verify effectiveness</li>
					</ol>

					<h3>Certification & Standards</h3>
					<p>Our penetration testing follows industry standards including:</p>
					<ul class="cert-list">
						<li>OWASP Testing Guide</li>
						<li>PTES (Penetration Testing Execution Standard)</li>
						<li>NIST SP 800-115</li>
						<li>PCI DSS Requirements (if applicable)</li>
					</ul>

					<div class="cta-box">
						<h3>Pricing</h3>
						<p>Starting from $8,000 for basic web application tests. Full network penetration testing from $15,000.</p>
						<a href="/quote" class="btn-primary">Request a Quote</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="service-detail" id="compliance">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="service-content">
				<div class="service-text">
					<h2>‚úÖ EN 18031-1 Compliance Testing</h2>
					<p class="lead">Ensure compliance with the European standard EN 18031-1 for cybersecurity in critical infrastructure and industrial control systems.</p>
					
					<h3>About EN 18031-1</h3>
					<p>EN 18031-1 is the European standard for cybersecurity requirements and assessment methods for industrial automation and control systems (IACS). This standard is critical for organizations operating:</p>
					<ul class="feature-list">
						<li>Critical infrastructure (energy, water, transportation)</li>
						<li>Manufacturing and industrial facilities</li>
						<li>Process control systems</li>
						<li>SCADA systems</li>
						<li>Building automation systems</li>
					</ul>

					<h3>Our Compliance Services</h3>
					<ul class="feature-list">
						<li><strong>Gap Analysis:</strong> Comprehensive assessment of current security posture against EN 18031-1 requirements</li>
						<li><strong>Risk Assessment:</strong> Identify and evaluate cybersecurity risks to industrial systems</li>
						<li><strong>Security Architecture Review:</strong> Evaluate network segmentation, access controls, and defense-in-depth</li>
						<li><strong>Policy Development:</strong> Create and update security policies aligned with EN 18031-1</li>
						<li><strong>Technical Controls Assessment:</strong> Evaluate firewalls, IDS/IPS, authentication mechanisms</li>
						<li><strong>Incident Response Planning:</strong> Develop procedures specific to industrial systems</li>
						<li><strong>Documentation & Reporting:</strong> Comprehensive compliance documentation for audits</li>
						<li><strong>Training & Awareness:</strong> Staff training on EN 18031-1 requirements</li>
					</ul>

					<h3>Compliance Process</h3>
					<ol class="process-list">
						<li><strong>Initial Assessment:</strong> Document current state and identify gaps</li>
						<li><strong>Roadmap Development:</strong> Create prioritized plan to achieve compliance</li>
						<li><strong>Implementation Support:</strong> Guide security control implementation</li>
						<li><strong>Testing & Validation:</strong> Verify controls meet EN 18031-1 requirements</li>
						<li><strong>Documentation:</strong> Prepare compliance evidence and reports</li>
						<li><strong>Ongoing Monitoring:</strong> Maintain compliance through regular assessments</li>
					</ol>

					<h3>Key Compliance Areas</h3>
					<div class="compliance-grid">
						<div class="compliance-item">
							<h4>Asset Management</h4>
							<p>Inventory and classification of IACS components</p>
						</div>
						<div class="compliance-item">
							<h4>Access Control</h4>
							<p>Identity management and authorization mechanisms</p>
						</div>
						<div class="compliance-item">
							<h4>Network Security</h4>
							<p>Segmentation, monitoring, and intrusion detection</p>
						</div>
						<div class="compliance-item">
							<h4>System Hardening</h4>
							<p>Configuration management and patch management</p>
						</div>
						<div class="compliance-item">
							<h4>Monitoring & Logging</h4>
							<p>Security event detection and incident response</p>
						</div>
						<div class="compliance-item">
							<h4>Business Continuity</h4>
							<p>Backup, recovery, and resilience planning</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="cta-box">
						<h3>Pricing</h3>
						<p>EN 18031 compliance projects typically range from $5,000 to $20,000+ depending on system complexity.</p>
						<a href="/quote" class="btn-primary">Request a Quote</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="all-services">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Additional Services</h2>
			<div class="additional-services">
				<div class="add-service">
					<h3>Security Awareness Training</h3>
					<p>Educate your team on cybersecurity best practices and threat awareness.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="add-service">
					<h3>Incident Response</h3>
					<p>24/7 emergency response and forensic investigation services.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="add-service">
					<h3>Security Consulting</h3>
					<p>Strategic guidance on security architecture and governance.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="add-service">
					<h3>Managed Security Services</h3>
					<p>Ongoing security monitoring and management as a service.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="cta-banner">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Ready to Enhance Your Security?</h2>
			<p>Let's discuss your specific security needs and create a custom solution</p>
			<a href="/quote" class="btn-large btn-primary">Request a Quote</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.page-header {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark-bg) 0%, #0d1b2a 100%);
		padding: 4rem 0;
		text-align: center;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
	}

	.page-header h1 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		color: var(--secondary-color);
	}

	.page-header p {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		color: var(--text-gray);
	}

	.service-detail {
		padding: 5rem 0;
	}

	.alt-bg {
		background: var(--dark-card);
	}

	.service-content {
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.service-text h2 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		color: var(--text-light);
	}

	.lead {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		color: var(--text-gray);
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.service-text h3 {
		font-size: 1.75rem;
		margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem;
		color: var(--secondary-color);
	}

	.service-text h4 {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		margin: 1.5rem 0 0.5rem;
		color: var(--text-light);
	}

	.service-text p {
		color: var(--text-gray);
		line-height: 1.8;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.feature-list,
	.cert-list {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 1.5rem 0;
	}

	.feature-list li,
	.cert-list li {
		padding: 0.75rem 0;
		padding-left: 2rem;
		position: relative;
		color: var(--text-gray);
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.feature-list li::before {
		content: "‚úì";
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: var(--accent-green);
		font-weight: bold;
		font-size: 1.2rem;
	}

	.cert-list li::before {
		content: "‚ñ∏";
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: var(--secondary-color);
		font-weight: bold;
	}

	.feature-list strong {
		color: var(--text-light);
	}

	.process-list {
		padding-left: 1.5rem;
		margin: 1.5rem 0;
	}

	.process-list li {
		color: var(--text-gray);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.process-list strong {
		color: var(--text-light);
	}

	.compliance-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin: 2rem 0;
	}

	.compliance-item {
		background: var(--dark-bg);
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 0.5rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
	}

	.compliance-item h4 {
		color: var(--secondary-color);
		margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
	}

	.compliance-item p {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
	}

	.cta-box {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%);
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 1rem;
		margin: 3rem 0;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.cta-box h3 {
		margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
		color: var(--text-light);
	}

	.cta-box p {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		color: var(--text-light);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}

	.all-services {
		padding: 5rem 0;
		background: var(--dark-bg);
	}

	.all-services h2 {
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		color: var(--text-light);
	}

	.additional-services {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.add-service {
		background: var(--dark-card);
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 0.5rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
	}

	.add-service:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 163, 255, 0.2);
		border-color: var(--secondary-color);
	}

	.add-service h3 {
		color: var(--secondary-color);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.add-service p {
		color: var(--text-gray);
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.cta-banner {
		padding: 6rem 0;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%);
		text-align: center;
	}

	.cta-banner h2 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.cta-banner p {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		opacity: 0.9;
	}

	.btn-large {
		padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
		border-radius: 0.5rem;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 600;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		transition: all 0.3s;
		display: inline-block;
		background: var(--text-light);
		color: var(--primary-color);
	}

	.btn-large:hover {
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.page-header h1 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.service-text h2 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.compliance-grid,
		.additional-services {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
